<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
  <div xml:id="Aink201-kilavi">
      <p type="edition"> notu malar varaiviṉkaṇ cevili kēṭkum āṟṟāl talaimakaṭ ṭōḻikk* aṟattoṭu nilai kuṟitt* uraittatu. </p>

      <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> What the heroine told the confidante regarding the “standing up with virtue” [i.e., revealing the truth], in [the context] of marrying a stranger, by a manner in which foster mother [could] listen. </p>
      </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink201">
<l>aṉṉāy vāḻivēṇ ṭaṉṉai yeṉṉai</l>
<l>tāṉu malaintā ṉemakkun taḻaiyāyiṉa</l>
<l>poṉvī maṇiyarum piṉavē</l>
<l>yeṉṉa maraṅko lavarcāra lavvē</l>
      </lg>
        <lg xml:lang="en">
          <l>Oh Mother, please Mother, </l>
          <l>What my lord himself wore, </l>
          <l>which also became the foliage for me,</l>
          <l>had golden mature blossoms and sapphire buds.</l>
          <l rend="space">“What trees grow upon his mountain slope?</l>

          
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
